<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= post.title %> - 我的个人博客</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="brand-mark gradient-button" aria-label="Poppis">
        <span class="gradient-text">Poppis</span>
      </a>
      <div class="header-content">
        <div class="brand-block">
          <p class="brand-kicker">Article View</p>
          <h1 class="logo"><a href="/">我的博客</a></h1>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="/">首页</a>
          <a href="/about">关于我</a>
          <% if (user) { %>
            <a href="/poppis-console/dashboard">后台管理</a>
          <% } %>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="main">
    <div class="container article-shell">
      <div class="article-layout">
        <article class="post-detail">
          <div class="article-intro">
            <p class="article-kicker">Essay</p>
            <h1 class="post-detail-title"><%= post.title %></h1>
            <div class="post-detail-meta">
              <% if (post.category_name) { %>
                <span class="category"><%= post.category_name %></span>
              <% } %>
              <span class="date"><%= new Date(post.created_at).toLocaleDateString('zh-CN', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></span>
              <span class="views"><%= post.views %> 次阅读</span>
            </div>
            <% if (post.tags && post.tags.length > 0) { %>
              <div class="post-detail-tags">
                <% post.tags.forEach(tag => { %>
                  <a href="/tag/<%= tag.slug %>" class="tag"><%= tag.name %></a>
                <% }) %>
              </div>
            <% } %>
          </div>

          <% if (post.cover_image) { %>
            <img src="<%= post.cover_image %>" alt="<%= post.title %>" class="post-detail-cover">
          <% } %>

          <div class="post-detail-content">
            <%- post.content %>
          </div>
        </article>

        <aside class="article-rail">
          <div class="rail-card">
            <p class="section-kicker">Reading Notes</p>
            <h3>这一页适合慢慢读。</h3>
            <p>如果你是第一次来到这里，可以先从首页回看最近更新，再决定要不要继续沿着分类和标签展开。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rail-card">
            <p class="section-kicker">Article Info</p>
            <ul class="rail-list">
              <li>发布时间：<%= new Date(post.created_at).toLocaleDateString('zh-CN') %></li>
              <li>阅读量：<%= post.views %></li>
              <% if (post.category_name) { %>
                <li>分类：<%= post.category_name %></li>
              <% } %>
            </ul>
            <a href="/" class="btn btn-ghost rail-button">返回首页</a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="container footer-grid">
      <div>
        <p class="footer-kicker">继续阅读</p>
        <h3>内容会慢一点，但尽量更耐看。</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/">返回首页</a>
        <a href="/about">关于作者</a>
      </div>
      <p class="footer-copy">&copy; 2026 我的个人博客.</p>
      <p class="footer-copy footer-beian">
        <a href="https://beian.mps.gov.cn/#/query/webSearch?code=61030402000136" rel="noreferrer" target="_blank" class="beian-link">
          <img src="/images/beian-badge.svg" alt="公安备案图标" class="beian-icon">
          <span>陕公网安备61030402000136号</span>
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
